00065 void GenericDataTest_MinDPH::DataSetByIndexTest()
00066 {
00067         // Check that a MinDP will be read-in completely before being accessed through GenericData.
00068         DataSet* dp = data->DataSet(0,0);
00069         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dp);
00070         const DataSetHeader& dph = dp->Header();
00071 
00072         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dph.GetName() == L"acquired data");
00073         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dph.GetDataStartFilePos() != 0);
00074         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dph.GetNameValParamCnt() == 2);
00075         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dph.GetRowSize() == sizeof(u_int16_t));
00076         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dph.GetDataSize() == sizeof(u_int16_t)*100);
00077         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dph.GetRowCnt() == 100);
00078         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dph.GetColumnCnt() == 1);
00079         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dph.GetDataStartFilePos() == 0x3a0);
00080 
00081         // Check the data group name value pairs
00082         ParameterNameValueTypeConstIt nvpBegin, nvpEnd;
00083         dph.GetNameValIterators(nvpBegin, nvpEnd);
00084         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin != nvpEnd);
00085         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetName() == L"Scanner");
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetValueText() == L"M10");
00087         ++nvpBegin;
00088         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin != nvpEnd);
00089         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetName() == L"Pixel Size");
00090         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetValueFloat() == 0.051f);
00091         ++nvpBegin;
00092         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin == nvpEnd);
00093 
00094         // Check the data set columns
00095         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dph.GetColumnInfo(0).GetColumnType() == UShortColType);
00096         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dph.GetColumnInfo(0).GetSize() == sizeof(u_int16_t));
00097 
00098         dp->Delete();
00099 }

00173 void GenericDataTest_MinDPH::DataSetNamesTest()
00174 {
00175         // By name
00176         std::vector<std::wstring> names;
00177         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_THROW(data->DataSetNames(L"none", names), affymetrix_calvin_exceptions::DataGroupNotFoundException);
00178         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(data->DataSetNames(L"First Data Cube", names));
00179         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(names.size() == 1);
00180         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(names[0] == L"acquired data");
00181 
00182         // By index
00183         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_THROW(data->DataSetNames(1, names), affymetrix_calvin_exceptions::DataGroupNotFoundException);
00184         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(data->DataSetNames(0, names));
00185         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(names.size() == 1);
00186         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(names[0] == L"acquired data");
00187 }
